dct_title_s: Udrone Irlandiae: in Caterlag Baronia.; Vdrone Irlandiae in Caterlag Baronia.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Includes inscription reading "Per Gerardum Mercatorem cum priuilegio." Title cartouche is surrounded by fruit. Does not match any states listed in Van der Krogt. From the Appendix Atlas of the British Isles and Northern Europe, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map: 34 x 27 cm.
dct_creator_sm: Hondius, Hendrik, 1597-1651. Appendix Atlas of the British Isles and Northern Europe
Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664. Appendix Atlas of the British Isles and Northern Europe
